dia_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-9Vf","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":36402,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/05\/30\/duha-four-rakaat\/","url_meta":{"origin":38145,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Duha: Four raka\u2019at for Allah, He will suffice your day","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 30, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"\u2018Uqbah ibn \u2018Amir reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah Almighty says: O son of Adam, suffice Me with four cycles of prayer at the beginning of the morning and by them I will suffice you for the rest of your day.\u201d Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25820,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/01\/28\/salat-private-conversation\/","url_meta":{"origin":38145,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Salat: Believer in private conversation with Allah in prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 28, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, the believer in prayer is in a private conversation with his Lord. Let him not spit in front of him, nor to his right side, but rather to his left side or beneath his feet.\u201d Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34807,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/12\/25\/falaq-nas-salat\/","url_meta":{"origin":38145,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Salat: Recite al-Falaq and al-Nas after prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 25, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"\u2018Uqbah ibn \u2018Amir reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, commanded me to recite the two chapters of refuge, al-Falaq and al-Nas, at the end of every prayer. Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2903 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Ibn Hajar \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064f\u0642\u0652\u0628\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0645\u0650\u0631\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064e\u0646\u0650\u064a \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":12952,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/03\/18\/between-two-calls-to-prayer\/","url_meta":{"origin":38145,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Nawafil: Sunan prayer between Adhan and Iqamah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 18, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mughaffil reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"Between every two calls to prayer is a prayer. Between every two calls to prayer is a prayer.\" Then, on the third time, the Prophet said, \"For whoever wishes.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 627, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 838 Grade:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15454,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/28\/khushu-will-become-rare\/","url_meta":{"origin":38145,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Khusu&#8217;: Reverence for Allah to become rare","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 28, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Darda reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe first thing to be taken from this nation will be humble reverence, until you will not see anyone in it with reverence.\u201d Source: Musnad al-Sha\u0304miyyi\u0304n lil-T\u0323abara\u0304ni\u0304 1561 Grade: Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0627\u0644\u062f\u064e\u0651\u0631\u0652\u062f\u064e\u0627\u0621\u0650 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0628\u0650\u064a\u064e\u0651\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26206,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/04\/15\/protect-salat-with-sutrah\/","url_meta":{"origin":38145,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Sutrah: Protect prayer from disruption with barrier","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 15, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Dharr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIf one of you stands for prayer, he is screened by a barrier\u00a0if there is an object before him like the back of saddle. If there is nothing like the back of a saddle before him,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaeli